reviews.text:
I enjoyed FolkArt's Rudolph on Acid, so Pony on Acid was an easy choice to mix his Pony on Acid.  This recipe far surpasses Rudolph.  I've not vaped the SMAK's commercial version, so I can't compare that aspect and after vaping this I feel no need to do so.  (Sorry FolkArt, but I subbed JF Strawberry Sweet for Health Cabin Fresh Strawberry at the same percentage... always missing one concentrate!)  Even so, this is absolutely brilliant, FolkArt!  I love how hints of graham and pineapple peak through this creamy gooey strawberry mix.  &#xD;
&#xD;
Super big thank you for sharing this recipe and for the detailed description - that really helps us less experienced mixers to understand what is going and why you chose each concentrate.  When I see a mix with such detailed description, I see it as a sign of pride in their creation and that the creator actually cares about helping other mixers become better mixers.  This is going straight into my favorites folder.  And, I will pick up that HC Fresh Strawberry at some point in the near future so that I can mix it as you intended.  But for now, I couldn't be more pleased.
